{"tid":2237441,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"侵侵： 我想要一個規模大撚過共和同民主黨提議既刺激方案","createTime":"2020-10-10T09:26:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-10T18:24:30.000Z","uid":48083,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"f9fc2f42c51e795697dc20ed3ca85bef760e2e93","tid":2237441,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T09:26:14.000Z","msg":"President Donald Trump said he wants an even bigger stimulus than what Democrats have offered so far, yet another turnabout in his position and one that seemed to undercut his own negotiators.<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;I would like to see a bigger stimulus package, frankly, than either the Democrats or the Republicans are offering,&rdquo; Trump said on Rush Limbaugh&rsquo;s radio program, saying he&rsquo;s going in the &ldquo;exact opposite&rdquo; direction from his earlier stances.<br />\n<br />\n⋯⋯⋯Treasury Secretary Steven Mnuchin headed into talks with House Speaker Nancy Pelosi on Friday carrying a White House offer of $1.8 trillion for economic stimulus, according to people familiar with the matter. The two spoke for about 30 minutes and Mnuchin&rsquo;s proposal &ldquo;attempted to address some of the concerns Democrats have,&rdquo; Pelosi spokesman Drew Hammill said on Twitter.<br />\n<br />\nPelosi has proposed a $2.2 trillion plan, down from the $3.4 trillion package the House passed in May, but the differences between the two sides involve more than money. They also differ on how it should be spent.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2020-10-09/trump-has-approved-a-revised-stimulus-plan-kudlow-says\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2020-10-09%2Ftrump-has-approved-a-revised-stimulus-plan-kudlow-says&d=qh2qPVBUtyR5HqmPKg%2BIDIdddMXd0Scb%2F0m37zAf7q8%3D&h=0190cd9d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2020-10-09/trump-has-approved-a-revised-stimulus-plan-kudlow-says</a>"},{"pid"